oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Registration certificate and pension card of Lawrence Ray Estep
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Registration certificate and pension card of Lawrence Ray Estep of Giles County, Tennessee. Estep served in Recruit Co. 20, 5th Training Battn., 156th Depot Brig. at Camp Jackson, South Carolina. He received a medical discharge in February 1918 for heart trouble.
